<div id="review_2375996664" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2375996664" />
    <a title="Mandy" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/13483840-mandy"><img alt="Mandy" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/f_50x66-6a03a5c12233c941481992b82eea8d23.png" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2375996664?book_show_action=true">May 04, 2018</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Mandy" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Mandy" href="/user/show/13483840-mandy">Mandy</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/13483840-mandy?shelf=giveaways">giveaways</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2375996664" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8999971919809389062">I won this book in a giveaway. The concept intrigued me. I enjoy time travel stories and the idea of going back to the moment you most regret seemed interesting. I thought this was well written but it didn&apos;t keep me wanting to keep reading to find out more so thought three stars is fair. I didn&apos;t have to force myself to finish I was curious to see what else would change in the Ana&apos;s life as the book progressed but feel like I would have enjoyed more if it was fleshed out into a full novel rather</span>
  <span id="freeText8999971919809389062" style="display:none">I won this book in a giveaway. The concept intrigued me. I enjoy time travel stories and the idea of going back to the moment you most regret seemed interesting. I thought this was well written but it didn't keep me wanting to keep reading to find out more so thought three stars is fair. I didn't have to force myself to finish I was curious to see what else would change in the Ana's life as the book progressed but feel like I would have enjoyed more if it was fleshed out into a full novel rather than a series.</span>
  <a data-text-id="8999971919809389062" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


