      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Sahani Perera, The Book Sherpa " class="user" itemprop="url" name="Sahani Perera, The Book Sherpa " href="/user/show/70090136-sahani-perera-the-book-sherpa">Sahani Perera, The Book Sherpa </a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2630454912" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6832634545754504405">A though-provoking inspirational read about the philosophies of life played by an unexpected person. The author&apos;s aim of reflecting the perfect way of life, and a second chance to live is well served. Even though this read belongs to the time travel fantasy read, I believe it has something to say to everyone!</span>
  <span id="freeText6832634545754504405" style="display:none">A though-provoking inspirational read about the philosophies of life played by an unexpected person. The author's aim of reflecting the perfect way of life, and a second chance to live is well served. Even though this read belongs to the time travel fantasy read, I believe it has something to say to everyone!</span>
