<span id="freeTextContainer8556172047551967664">Thought-provoking – Story<br/>Well the idea is not unique of travel back in times, but the way this book brings it up is surely different and a likable path to travel back in times. The idea of an opportunity to changes back one thing in your past that you regret, is surely good, but the warning and the realization or outcomes of that one decision is the real highlight. Anya Jones a doctor takes that journey of traveling back and changing her decision to drop out of school and surprising the outcome </span>
  <span id="freeText8556172047551967664" style="display:none">Thought-provoking – Story<br />Well the idea is not unique of travel back in times, but the way this book brings it up is surely different and a likable path to travel back in times. The idea of an opportunity to changes back one thing in your past that you regret, is surely good, but the warning and the realization or outcomes of that one decision is the real highlight. Anya Jones a doctor takes that journey of traveling back and changing her decision to drop out of school and surprising the outcome was different than what is expected. Well, it’s easy to say or think that your choices, decides your course of life, but difficult to predict what would have changed, if you would have made a different choice.<br /></span>
